Description: C++ client library for etcd v3 API (development files)
 etcd-cpp-apiv3 is a C++ client library for etcd's v3 API.
 Provides synchronous (SyncClient) access to etcd key-value store.
 .
 This package contains headers, shared library, and cmake config files.
